OOC: Kslawdogg, a lot of wrestlers have come straight from Pro Football,
the Rock is just one of many, and he stole the Rock Bottom from someone
else in turn, barely any moves are made up nowadays, he just uses a
Sambo Suplex, (or Orange Suplex? can't remember) I dislike the Rock, but
he is good for the buisness, so I tolerate him, but you are way wrong
when you say that WCW wrestlers have no character, the only WCW
wrestlers that WWF got were the rookies, because Mchamahon is to cheap
to buy the big names like Sting, Jarrett, and Steiner. Don't forget that
Chris Benoit, Chris Jericho, Steven Regal, all learned their trade in
the WCW.
